ling algorithm, which is more accurate\ncompared to the sequential sampling. The main novel ingredients of our approach\nconsist of: defining appropriate permanent basis functions and the\ncorresponding residual; setting up a proper posterior distribution; and\nsampling the posteriors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Feb 2017 20:28:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-13"}
